    "ambiguity_status": "minor",
    "intended": "Let $R_3(n)$ be the minimal $m$ such that if the edges of the $3$-uniform hypergraph on $m$ vertices are $2$-coloured then there is a monochromatic copy of the complete $3$-uniform hypergraph on $n$ vertices.\n\nIs there some constant $c>0$ such that\\[R_3(n) \\geq 2^{2^{cn}}?\\]",
